high_descs: Turn right and walk to the white, round table, turning to face it.
Pick up the knife that is in the middle of the table.
Move the lettuce in the middle of the table slightly to the side.
Slice the loaf of bread that is in between the other two.
Holding the knife, turn left and walk over to the silver trash can.
Throw the knife in the trash.
Turn around and walk back over to the white, round table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf you cut earlier.
Turn around and walk towards the black fridge.
Open the fridge, put the slice of bread in and close the door. Wait and then take the slice back out.
Turn around and walk to the silver trash can.
Throw the slice of bread in the trash.
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of bread, chill it and throw it away.

Walk towards the round table
